CREATE VIEW BUSINESS_RULES.COMPONENT_S_PSA_C_ARCHITECTURE_HISTORYVIEW
AS

  SELECT 
    bo."BK Component",    -- Business Key for Hub Component
    bo."LDTS_FROM",             -- technische Gültigkeit
    bo."LDTS_TO",             -- technische Gültigkeit
    bo."Cluster",         -- PACKAGE_AUTOSARCLUSTER from Satellite Component > PSA > AutoSAR
    bo."Modul"            -- PACKAGE_SHORTNAME from Satellite Component > PSA > AutoSAR
  FROM (
SELECT
    H00_H_COMPONENT.COMPONENT_BK AS "BK Component",
    S0000_S_COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR.COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR_LTH LDTS_FROM,     
    COALESCE(LEAD(S0000_S_COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR.COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR_LTH) OVER (PARTITION BY H00_H_COMPONENT.COMPONENT_BK ORDER BY S0000_S_COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR.COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR_LTH asc ), DATETIME2FROMPARTS(9999,12,31,23,59,59,0,0)) AS LDTS_TO,    
    S0000_S_COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR.PACKAGE_AUTOSARCLUSTER AS "Cluster",
    S0000_S_COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR.PACKAGE_SHORTNAME AS "Modul"
  FROM   DATAVAULT.H_COMPONENT H00_H_COMPONENT 
  JOIN DATAVAULT.S_COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR_H 
  	S0000_S_COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR
    	ON (H00_H_COMPONENT.COMPONENT_H = S0000_S_COMPONENT_S_PSA_R_XMLCOMPONENT_XMLINTERFACE_U_BUSINESS_RULES_F_AUTOSAR.COMPONENT_H)
  ) bo
